divs: sighting detailsi was taking some sky pictures at 10:00am this morning (03\06\2006) and got these two pictures with the same objects in them. i took twelve shots and these were the only two with any objects in them. the second picture (the one with the objects behind a tree branch) was taken less than a minute after the first one was taken. the camera was pointed in an easterly direction and the objects were moving in nw direction. in the past six months i have captured objects of this kind and also white round ones and also white mixed with other colors. with the enlargements there are a total of four pictures. this is the fourth picture.
